{"tid":5593,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"去日本旅行，你會用邊款上網卡？","createTime":"2016-11-27T03:27:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-08T02:13:10.000Z","uid":28393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a68e92fb4d91a18349daf37a49250496d904bd5d","tid":5593,"uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我拋磚引玉先<br />\n目前市面上的卡大致分為(靠睇APN來區分)<br />\n,唔知咩係APN的話，甚至搞亂APN同VPN 的，不如google下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歷史悠久的 <a href=\"http://umobile.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fumobile.jp&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=7bd8e9c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">umobile.jp</a><br />\n大陸出品 <a href=\"http://香港包裝的mvno.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8C%85%E8%A3%9D%E7%9A%84mvno.net&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=0449d854\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">香港包裝的mvno.net</a><br />\n今年新出場 whatsApp任用的freetel.link<br />\n台灣出品 賣點無限任用的 <a href=\"http://mineo-d.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmineo-d.jp&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=d877f778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mineo-d.jp</a><br />\n日本自遊易 myxxxxmarket <a href=\"http://代理的vdm.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%9A%84vdm.jp&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f38e396f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">代理的vdm.jp</a><br />\n各香港公司出品的漫遊卡(<a href=\"http://mobile.lte.three.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmobile.lte.three.com.hk&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f6982a6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mobile.lte.three.com.hk</a> / MORE/ 3gnet..etc) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好只係識docomo, 要認住啲公司先得，因為質素真係可以很大分別。<br />\n<br />\n大家上次去日本又用邊款呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742d55df645e75371cec103c365539040f58c2cf","tid":5593,"uid":8909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"So-net 幾快"},{"pid":"fdf9c9513576e61927de5258d4aa75697883dd5e","tid":5593,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:36:58.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf489c4777810850d929306cf7a927f1d90b860","tid":5593,"uid":22247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/115105_d1f6a718dc34bc2b1a1e6af0f4638c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F115105_d1f6a718dc34bc2b1a1e6af0f4638c21.jpg&h=202e1540&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45MU09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45MU09.jpg&h=d6a3fc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mvno.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmvno.net&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=be9ff114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">mvno.net</a><br />\n<br />\n人在日本答你"},{"pid":"0345bda7b1d9d891dd4a6aa75d7d770eb950d9fd","tid":5593,"uid":2601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T03:55:02.000Z","msg":"鴨記 80蚊 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://umobole.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fumobole.jp&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=7e051c7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">umobole.jp</a>"},{"pid":"8d47e8f2ee36accc73d1805e3b98cea5bf071723","tid":5593,"uid":22247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"Wifi 蛋完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BzZ31v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src