\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc5ebea5a494a2f37bb6093856ef67f573d0c73","tid":5593,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/27/115105_d1f6a718dc34bc2b1a1e6af0f4638c21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F27%2F115105_d1f6a718dc34bc2b1a1e6af0f4638c21.jpg&h=202e1540&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45MU09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45MU09.jpg&h=d6a3fc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://mvno.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmvno.net&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=be9ff114\" target=\"_blank\">http://mvno.net</a><br />\n<br />\n人在日本答你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n速度有幾多左右呢？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢架喎呢張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f189c2ea085c579df873b6756d4590bac273e5","tid":5593,"uid":58,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:35:40.000Z","msg":"Studio a果張，百幾蚊2.2g 4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61afec37c163df7a9d0922281d71d9b60876b2d","tid":5593,"uid":22919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T08:43:35.000Z","msg":"鴨記買過張有個海豚樣果張  垃圾到無人有  whatsapp 聲相都聲唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3288b2b004a14fd9856fa105de9221b264b64286","tid":5593,"uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:41:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>SIM卡係咪真係打唔到電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前唔知邊單新聞有巴打講過 所以從不考慮sim卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打唔到架，一定打唔到。日本電話要實名登記和係日本有在留卡等證件先登記到。意思遊客只有data card 或者同啲日本公司租電話用。"},{"pid":"8ac30836fb577ac09a714ffa2855ce891bf05c61","tid":5593,"uid":28393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T18:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Studio a果張，百幾蚊2.2g 4g<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://應該都係umobile.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%87%89%E8%A9%B2%E9%83%BD%E4%BF%82umobile.jp&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=d925f5a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">應該都係umobile.jp</a> 個APN? 有錯指證"},{"pid":"f8dbe32ac6d6a0f060835c6184eda68cc15eae8c","tid":5593,"uid":15883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T19:03:13.000Z","msg":"去過3次日本都係用b mobile<br />\n第一次要用當地手機開卡，限速380kbps <br />\n第二次唔洗開卡，可以用LTE不過限速<br />\n今年去就變左無限速限量LTE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭兩次都要寄去酒店<br />\n第三次就喺Amazon買，平1000円同埋可以喺便利店拎唔洗麻煩酒店職員<br />\n除左冇得一落機就上得網同埋略貴之外，我好滿意呢張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n十二月尾都會去日本，今次想試下香港啲卡但係驚中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bee0b94520e77870187949bc4ab44f464ba267","tid":5593,"uid":638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T20:07:00.000Z","msg":"去9日10日有冇推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac8260a8360e5fa223d53b37dd6ebd050605127","tid":5593,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T20:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.liontravel.com/event/member/news_img/542015122909575496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.liontravel.co