d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmMW%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=f6982a6f\" target=\"_blank\">http://mobile.lte.three.com.hk</a> / MORE/ 3gnet..etc) <br />\n<br />\n大家唔好只係識docomo, 要認住啲公司先得，因為質素真係可以很大分別。<br />\n<br />\n大家上次去日本又用邊款呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nbmobile<br />\n用自己部pocket wifi"},{"pid":"a3fe8076d285add4bc690688335bea29afe01d1d","tid":5593,"uid":39032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T06:59:11.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"f95611934a402ab83a7cd9bab4e4709c3cc8251f","tid":5593,"uid":2014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"租左banana 到時再報告 35蚊日"},{"pid":"400ce5c1be5a709a03f04e479bec5ca44a595c0b","tid":5593,"uid":44844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:08:41.000Z","msg":"上amazon 訂sonet 卡<br />\n去到係lawson 拎"},{"pid":"2a445591b6f60715c4d26142f76b0609d29d3391","tid":5593,"uid":807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/151217_86094dc953e73a96c64b8eaf712654f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F151217_86094dc953e73a96c64b8eaf712654f5.jpg&h=16c29c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張點樣，我見到鴨記有呢張既8日不限速放題版賣100<br />\n有無巴打用過速度如何？<br />\n我遲啲一月去關西八日打算買呢張，因為SMT7日卡好貴"},{"pid":"8b7160ea93ff772a650d5ad7a88f01fcbf1405ec","tid":5593,"uid":40026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/30/151217_86094dc953e73a96c64b8eaf712654f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F30%2F151217_86094dc953e73a96c64b8eaf712654f5.jpg&h=64ecbaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢張點樣，我見到鴨記有呢張既8日不限速放題版賣100<br />\n有無巴打用過速度如何？<br />\n我遲啲一月去關西八日打算買呢張，因為SMT7日卡好貴</blockqu